{"tid":2454363,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"31歲男子涉訛稱代購玩具及動漫騙財被捕","createTime":"2021-03-20T07:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T11:48:48.000Z","uid":41404,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"73bb195b5ba96545110a842f9cc486551eb95001","tid":2454363,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:42:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581634-20210320.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581634-20210320.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDGINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=e8cae8a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581634-20210320.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=16222cea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581634-20210320.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕一名31歲男子，懷疑在網上售賣玩具及動漫等貨物，收錢後失去聯絡，涉及款項75000元，有16名受害人。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，接獲懷疑網上騙案的報案，指一間網店去年3月至11月，在包括facebook、instagram及carousell等網上平台，表示可以代購動漫及模型等，並要求買家以轉數快等平台先付款，及後以疫情及貨品未到港等為由延遲交貨，之後更失去聯絡。"},{"pid":"b2bc10dde50aa120e137fb101a4df929d7571b09","tid":2454363,"uid":252588,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:45:20.000Z","msg":"呢D仆街拉撚哂就啱啦，毒撚錢都呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f0e514b9abe28dab79df4d777525791e1b4d0b","tid":2454363,"uid":193969,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:46:24.000Z","msg":"毒撚錢真係易呃，同買電子雞相果啲都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd1b228d24ed82ca76d4cdf5c7d7a8471837fcb","tid":2454363,"uid":242537,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:46:29.000Z","msg":"死仆街<br />\n起咗底未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.g